{"tid":1392301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生手足請入！（暑期活動支援小組）[重PO]","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:17:34.000Z","uid":295829,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8957c3b440369a8cdb4cbbb8be5377e60341da6","tid":1392301,"uid":295829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"近來積極參與「暑期活動」既的你地，有無覺得：<br />\n遇到麻煩，唔知點搵幫手？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或<br />\n屋企人唔明白你、甚至鬧爆你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或<br />\n暑期活動既唔如意令你心情低落/好嬲？或<br />\n成日自己發夢，無人陪/吹水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或<br />\n想識多啲同伴，交流暑假活動經歷同心得？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人是一名社工，三十零一歲，從事青少年工作多年，一直好支持年青人關心社會。眼見近來好多同學積極投入「暑期活動」，但往往有唔少困難，尤其中學生，要面對屋企、甚至家庭/交通/住宿/生活/法律／情緒等方面都有唔少壓大，而我都好想幫到大家手，同大家同行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此，本人希望組織一個「暑期活動支援小組」(TG Group)，希望十卜各位同學，幫各位提供 / 配對各類型的支援，亦希望透過個group，等大家知道你地並唔孤單，有好多戰友同你地一齊，group mate亦可以互相幫忙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家如果有興趣入既，就telegram我 @easonsir，同你地講兩句就加你入group 。<br />\n（第一次出PO，是希望接觸到有需要的人，有勞各位大大幫推一下！）<br />\n<br />\n註一: 此群組並不屬於任何社福機構，一切資料保密處理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n註二: 跟據香港法律，只有經過社工註冊局註冊的人才可自稱為社工，如有冒認即屬違法<br />\n註三: 此群組暫時只設中學部，希望可以集中支持年紀較細既巴打絲打。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chXarZd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchXarZd.jpg&h=1bbe421f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"239e35a55e77c488fb5fd341ff41bc8818608324","tid":1392301,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"中六畢業咗一個月<br />\n仲侵唔侵我入<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2542ea629ecb02e1be8c4dc04b292cb3a4ec89","tid":1392301,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"85700ac2b18e28a6f84409082cbaab4e770b704f","tid":1392301,"uid":295829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"239e35a55e77c488fb5fd341ff41bc8818608324","tid":1392301,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"中六畢業咗一個月<br />\n仲侵唔侵我入<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"中六升大一都計！找我吧~~"},{"pid":"a34f63b2704826b493624f2e75a0cf0817919c27","tid":1392301,"uid":211806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"6a36a4815331a2a0589dee46d41b64e28d8fa819","tid":1392301,"uid":211806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83ebb0aac21d72df155cebb7295e880f0730472b","tid":1392301,"uid":209808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f61199d5d6551c9b9cca0bb7eacc52113aab0ad1","tid":1392301,"uid":209808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"再pish"},{"pid":"a910160d1caf06d86528722bd4179c29c48285ec","tid":1392301,"uid":211806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"推完再推"},{"pid":"fdc26a5ee7e31c96c02706480e2c6dfe8e9b23b7","tid":1392301,"uid":214029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0b6b979a4f0b49ada9dc846b34aae7615b12091","tid":1392301,"uid":211806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"推呢個po上熱門！"},{"pid":"f72f3d86e759d0976f5ff49b142bcd66ea03fa76","tid":1392301,"uid":211806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ce1810866644dce637dea2ab3389a